     /// Measurement-definition epoch of the rows this build writes.
     ///
     /// Issue #812: version 1 counted every changed line, including the captured CI
     /// logs that `dev/log/issues/<n>/pulls/<n>/` bundles hold. In the `v0.300.0..HEAD`
